{"tid":494696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【比特幣電騙】女網友聲稱被捉走 男子被呃10萬元Bitcoin","createTime":"2017-12-10T02:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T04:34:57.000Z","uid":84436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b90b440105ed9eef7584fdff85a25e7bdeca4cd","tid":494696,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171210/57562451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57562451&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO2wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=368316e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57562451&h=b1a4f294\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171210/57562451</a><br />\n<br />\n一名姓黃31歲男子，早前在交友程式認識一名女子，雙方結識了幾個月。近日該女子幾次致電男主聲稱被人捉走，要求他付贖金。<br />\n<br />\n男事主不虞有詐，購買約值10萬港元的比特幣，並轉帳至一個戶口，但事後仍未能聯絡該女子，懷疑遇到騙案，凌晨零時許在慈雲山中心報警。<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由黃大仙警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n比特幣(Bitcoin)是一種加密貨幣，或稱虛擬貨幣，於2009年1月由日裔美國人中本哲史發明創立，至今已發展為最有代表性的虛擬貨幣之一，但相比貨幣，更像黃金，比特幣不受任何政府控制，因為它沒有發行機構，而是透過「挖礦」產生，並預計在2140年停止產生新的比特幣，最終數量將少於2,100萬個。<br />\n過去一年，除了大陸走資推升比特幣外，南韓是數一數二比特幣交易最活躍的國家。 比特幣周三升穿1.2萬美金創歷史新高後，有個別交易平台更出現超過1.5萬美元的交易紀錄。由於升勢急速，近期不斷有金融界猛人放話，比特幣風險極高，泡沫即將爆破，連美國聯儲局前主席格林斯潘都警告比特幣最終可能變得一文不值。<br />\n最近，美國監管當局通過比特幣期貨在芝加哥商品交易所（Chicago Mercantile Exchange，CME）及芝加哥期貨交易所（Chicago Board of Trade，CBOC）交易，芝商所及後公佈將在本月18日開始推出比特幣期貨，並將根據該所2016年推出、綜合多個主要比特幣交易平台計算得出的CF比特幣參考匯率（BRR）作每日結算；CBOC推出日期仍待公佈。"},{"pid":"1fe4f383a0f7ad52998b951fe2c4cd3510658906","tid":494696,"uid":73276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"10萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n佳佳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5b1b76faa21a10cdab588785b2376dc946a0cb","tid":494696,"uid":90704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:02:41.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093905fd903e2d597eb9ab78e690a4a4e81e419d","tid":494696,"uid":57776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"有冇咁撚on9，咁就冇左10萬<br />\n睇黎佳佳真係成功左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cbdf07c5a67ebf5774ba719cd085d56f47af48","tid":494696,"uid":130950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n佳佳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佳佳2日就套你攞錢 佢邊有咁好耐性"},{"pid":"00bba6998cf9fdb15b18387a7ea49cefd10daeed","tid":494696,"uid":160234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"係咪佳佳自爆得米嗰單？"},{"pid":"2f9b50ca5432f0e5cbde86ecf0313ccc7852b4ac","tid":494696,"uid":46759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佳佳只識叫你七仔入點,佢叻就唔會比人撚到依家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}